=Description=

"Blake Jones of Namaste Solar joins Alex and we learn what it means to be a democratic company. And why a founder like Blake shares all the decision making at Namaste. Every employee is a stockholder and every stockholder gets a vote. One vote. From Blake to the the installers, nobody gets more than a single vote. Blake claims it works better than the corporate structures most of us are used to and their incredible growth might be proof."
